      "content": "but my doctor wont even listen to me about supplements, he just says \"don't do it\". it's so frustrating. what if i just tapered off the warfarin slowly while i ramped up the garlic and the spinach shakes? if i'm doing both at the same time, wouldn't that act like a bridge so i don't have a gap in my protection? it seems like a much more natural way to transition if the garlic is already doing the thinning work.",
